{"data":[{"date":"16:02 10/07","title":"Ronaldo s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1 \u1edf \u0111\u00e2u trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Juventus?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/10/ronaldo-se-da-o-dau-trong-doi-hinh-juventus.PNG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Cristiano Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 th\u1eddi gian, d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin ph\u00e1t huy h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 100 tri\u1ec7u euro.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">4-3-1-2 v\u1edbi Ronaldo v\u00e0 Higuain \u0111\u00e1 cao nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc vi\u1ec5n c\u1ea3nh <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/lo-so-ao-cua-ronaldo-o-juventus-180-190540.html\" target=\"_blank\">Cristiano Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus</span>, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Gonzalo Higuain kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u00e2n s\u00fat 31 tu\u1ed5i r\u1ea5t vui v\u1edbi th\u00f4ng tin n\u00e0y. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i Juventus \u0111\u1ec3 s\u00e1t c\u00e1nh b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh CR7.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Cristiano Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus Allegri c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 n\u00e0o h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Cristiano Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus Allegri c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 n\u00e0o h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/10/Cristiano-Ronaldo-toi-Juventus-Allegri-co-the-van-hanh-so-do-nao-hinh-anh.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>4-3-1-2 v\u1edbi Ronaldo v\u00e0 Higuain \u0111\u00e1 cao nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Th\u1eadt tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi n\u1ebfu Ronaldo h\u1ee3p t\u00e1c v\u1edbi Higuain. H\u1ecd bi\u1ebft nhau r\u1ea5t r\u00f5, h\u1ecd ch\u01a1i kho\u1ea3ng 80 tr\u1eadn v\u1edbi nhau. Ronaldo v\u00e0 Higuain l\u00e0 2 trong s\u1ed1 nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, s\u1ef1 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p gi\u1eefa h\u1ecd r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i&rdquo;.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Ronaldo, HLV Massimiliano Allegri ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng 4-3-1-2 \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi. \u1ede tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa, Matuidi, Pjanic v\u00e0 Can l\u00e0 b\u1ed9 ba \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tin t\u01b0\u1edfng. Dybala ch\u01a1i \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed h\u1ed9 c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 cung c\u1ea5p b\u00f3ng cho Ronaldo v\u00e0 Higuain.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nDybala l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o v\u00f4 h\u1ea1n, nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ch\u1ecdc khe c\u1ee7a anh mang \u0111\u1ebfn r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho c\u00e1c ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o. V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 c\u1ee7a Dybala, Ronaldo v\u00e0 Higuain s\u1ebd c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNg\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1993 c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u00fat xa c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t, vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n hai ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u0169ng gi\u00fap anh ph\u00e1t huy h\u1ebft kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>4-3-3 v\u1edbi b\u1ed9 ba t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng Ronaldo, Higuain v\u00e0 Dybala</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 4-3-3 th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Allegri v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh. Theo \u0111\u00f3, Higuain, Dybala v\u00e0 Mandzukic l\u00e0 b\u1ed9 ba th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng. Khi Mandzukic kh\u00f4ng ra s\u00e2n th\u00ec Douglas Costa \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn thay th\u1ebf.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"4-3-3 voi bo ba tan cong Ronaldo, Higuain va Dybala\" title=\"4-3-3 v\u1edbi b\u1ed9 ba t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng Ronaldo, Higuain v\u00e0 Dybala\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/10/2.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>4-3-3 v\u1edbi b\u1ed9 ba t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng Ronaldo, Higuain v\u00e0 Dybala</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nS\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 v\u1edbi 3 m\u0169i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng gi\u00fap Juventus mang v\u1ec1 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. \u1ede m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Ronaldo, s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 4-3-3 h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd c\u00f2n ph\u00e1t huy nhi\u1ec1u hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 h\u01a1n n\u1eefa.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng g\u1ed3m 3 m\u0169i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, Ronaldo, Higuain v\u00e0 Dybala s\u00e1t c\u00e1nh b\u00ean nhau. CR7 ch\u01a1i b\u00ean c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i, Dybala ch\u01a1i c\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ed1i di\u1ec7n c\u00f2n Higuain ch\u01a1i \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed m\u0169i nh\u1ecdn. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t \u1edf ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, b\u1edfi v\u1eady s\u1ee9c t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng t\u1eeb h\u1ecd s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t kh\u1ee7ng&nbsp;khi\u1ebfp.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa, Juventus c\u00f3 chuy\u00ean gia l\u00e0m b\u00f3ng nh\u01b0 Pjanic, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y s\u1ebd c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i gi\u1eefa h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 v\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Bosnia duy tr\u00ec s\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn trong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, b\u1edfi v\u1eady anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m nhi\u1ec7m vai tr\u00f2 c\u1ea5p b\u00f3ng cho b\u1ed9 ba t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi Emre Can v\u00e0 Blaise Matuidi \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n, Juventus c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n qu\u00e1 lo l\u1eafng khi \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng. H\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 4 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f9ng s\u1ef1 tr\u1ee3 gi\u00fap c\u1ee7a 2 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng trong t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 ph\u00f2ng th\u1ee7.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>4-2-3-1 v\u1edbi Ronaldo \u0111\u00e1 cao nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Ronaldo, m\u1ecdi s\u1ef1 ch\u00fa \u00fd s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed5 d\u1ed3n v\u00e0o CR7. Khi \u0111\u00f3 t\u1ea7m \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a Higuain v\u00e0o l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Juventus s\u1ebd gi\u1ea3m \u0111i \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3, khi \u0111\u00f3 anh ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed9i \u0110KV\u0110 Serie A \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"4-2-3-1 voi Ronaldo da cao nhat tren hang cong\" title=\"4-2-3-1 v\u1edbi Ronaldo \u0111\u00e1 cao nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/10/3.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>4-2-3-1 v\u1edbi Ronaldo \u0111\u00e1 cao nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Higuain r\u1eddi Juventus, HLV Allegri kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i lo l\u1eafng b\u1edfi Ronaldo ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed do c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 31 tu\u1ed5i \u1edf l\u1ea1i. \u00d4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 4-2-3-1 v\u1edbi CR7 \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed cao nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi s\u1ef1 tr\u1ee3 gi\u00fap c\u1ee7a Dybala t\u1eeb ph\u00eda sau, Ronaldo s\u1ebd c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m. M\u00f9a v\u1eeba qua, ng\u00f4i sao 25 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra t\u1edbi 18 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho Higuain nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ec9 2 trong s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chuy\u1ec3n h\u00f3a th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi Ronaldo thay v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a Higuain, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ed1 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a Dybala \u1edf m\u00f9a t\u1edbi s\u1ebd t\u0103ng l\u00ean \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3. V\u1edbi Douglas Costa v\u00e0 Mario Mandzukic b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh Dybala, Juventus s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u00eam nh\u1eefng v\u0169 kh\u00ed \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>4-3-3 v\u1edbi Dybala, Ronaldo v\u00e0 Douglas Costa tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Higuain r\u1eddi Juventus ho\u1eb7c HLV Allegri kh\u00f4ng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina, \u00f4ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 4-3-3 v\u1edbi Paulo Dybala, Cristiano Ronaldo v\u00e0 Douglas Costa l\u00e0 3 m\u0169i nh\u1ecdn tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"4-3-3 voi Dybala, Ronaldo va Douglas Costa tren hang cong\" title=\"4-3-3 v\u1edbi Dybala, Ronaldo v\u00e0 Douglas Costa tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/10/4.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>4-3-3 v\u1edbi Dybala, Ronaldo v\u00e0 Douglas Costa tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng n\u00e0y, Ronaldo s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1 \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trung phong, Dybala v\u00e0 Douglas Costa ch\u01a1i \u1edf hai c\u00e1nh. N\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 CR7 s\u1edf h\u1eefu kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ch\u1ea1y ch\u1ed7 t\u1ed1t th\u00ec t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a Dybala v\u00e0 Douglas Costa, s\u1ef1 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p gi\u1eefa b\u1ed9 ba n\u00e0y s\u1ebd \u0111em l\u1ea1i s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMiralem Pjanic s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i cao nh\u1ea5t n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea5p b\u00f3ng cho b\u1ed9 ba t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Bosnia c\u0169ng c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t cao v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o, nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ch\u1ecdc khe s\u1eafc l\u1eb9m c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u00f9ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ch\u1ea1y ch\u1ed7 thi\u00ean t\u00e0i c\u1ee7a Ronaldo h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd gi\u00fap Juventus&nbsp;mang v\u1ec1 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1114","checkdouble":"190857"},{"date":"16:21 10/07","title":"4 l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 tin \u0110T Anh s\u1ebd v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/4-ly-do-de-tin-dt-anh-se-vo-dich-world-cup-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>N\u1eb1m \u1edf nh\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 m\u1ea1nh, \u0110T Anh \u0111ang ti\u1ebfn t\u1edbi s\u00e1t tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft h\u01a1n bao gi\u1edd h\u1ebft. V\u00e0 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 s\u1edf \u0111\u1ec3 tin r\u1eb1ng chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap v\u00e0ng World Cup s\u1ebd quay v\u1ec1 Anh sau 52 n\u0103m.</h2><br>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u01b0\u1edbc Anh v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup n\u0103m 1966, tuy nhi\u00ean k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 t\u1edbi nay qu\u00ea h\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a m\u00f4n th\u1ec3 thao vua \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e2ng cao chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap. N\u0103m nay \u1edf v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t nh\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea5u d\u1ec5, Tam s\u01b0 \u0111ang \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch. V\u00e0 \u0111\u00e2u l\u00e0 c\u01a1 s\u1edf \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tin v\u00e0o \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y?<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>Kh\u00f4ng \u00e1p l\u1ef1c b\u1edfi gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u0169ng gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 \u0111i tr\u01b0\u1edbc, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Southgate sang Nga m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u ni\u1ec1m hy v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00e2n Anh v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng chinh ph\u1ee5c chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u d\u1ec5 hi\u1ec3u b\u1edfi ngay c\u1ea3 th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 v\u00e0ng c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng Lampard, Gerrard, Ferdinand,\u2026 c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 \u0111\u00f3. \u0110T Anh tham d\u1ef1 World Cup l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh tr\u1ebb nh\u1ea5t trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed, v\u00ec th\u1ebf h\u1ecd \u00edt \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng x\u1ee9 s\u1edf S\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00f9 tung h\u00f4 v\u00e0 c\u0169ng \u00edt ph\u1ea3i mang theo nh\u1eefng \u00e1p l\u1ef1c n\u1eb7ng n\u1ec1 khi b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o gi\u1ea3i.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"4 l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 tin \u0110T Anh v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"4 l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 tin \u0110T Anh v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/8/4-ly-do-de-tin-DT-Anh-vo-dich-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>\u0110T Anh v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018<span style=\"font-family: arial, verdana, \" lucida=\"\" grande\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" text-align:=\"\" start;\"=\"\">\u00a0l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra khi h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ecbu nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ee9c \u00e9p</span></em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tham d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018 m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng mang theo nh\u1eefng g\u00e1nh n\u1eb7ng t\u00e2m l\u00fd, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y r\u00f5 c\u00e1c tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Anh \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3. Ngay c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 b\u1ecb nghi ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 phong \u0111\u1ed9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u di\u1ec5n ra nh\u01b0 ieran Trippier, Jesse Lingard v\u00e0 John Stones c\u0169ng \u0111ang c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n th\u0103ng hoa. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u1ecd thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e9o l\u00e9o v\u00e0 to\u00e1t l\u00ean s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin khi m\u00e0 \u00e1p l\u1ef1c t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t nh\u1ecf. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 g\u00f3p ph\u1ea7n gi\u00fap Tam s\u01b0 ti\u1ebfn s\u00e2u \u1edf gi\u1ea3i l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y v\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft s\u1ebd l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft g\u1eb7p Croatia v\u00e0o r\u1ea1ng s\u00e1ng th\u1ee9 N\u0103m t\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh kh\u00e1t danh hi\u1ec7u<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean d\u1eebng b\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1edbm \u1edf c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn nh\u01b0 EURO hay World Cup, ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh \u0111ang r\u1ea5t kh\u00e1t nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf. V\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd c\u0169ng \u0111ang mi\u1ec7t m\u00e0i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 mang c\u00fap v\u00e0ng tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ea3o qu\u1ed1c s\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00f9.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh \u0111\u00e3 cho th\u1ea5y tinh th\u1ea7n tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t Colombia thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7y s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 s\u1ef1 tinh qu\u00e1i. D\u00f9 c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n song c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Anh v\u1eabn cho th\u1ea5y m\u1ed9t tinh th\u1ea7n tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi v\u00e0 khao kh\u00e1t gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ean lo\u1ea1t s\u00fat lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u 11m, qua \u0111\u00f3 ph\u00e1 lu\u00f4n l\u1eddi nguy\u1ec1n th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Tam s\u01b0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed7i lo\u1ea1t s\u00fat 11m t\u1ea1i World Cup.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eefng th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Colombia hay Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n cho th\u1ea5y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup. C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh kh\u00f4ng s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u1eefng nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng mang t\u1edbi s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9t bi\u1ebfn tr\u00ean s\u00e2n \u0111\u1ea5u, nh\u01b0ng s\u1ee9c tr\u1ebb v\u00e0 kh\u00e1t khao chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 th\u1ee9 v\u0169 kh\u00ed c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 tr\u00ean h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh chinh ph\u1ee5c danh hi\u1ec7u cao qu\u00fd nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"DT Anh vao ban ket World Cup 2018 day thuyet phuc.\" title=\"\u0110T Anh v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 \u0111\u1ea7y thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/8/paul-scholes-pep-co-anh-huong-den-thanh-cong-cua-dt-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup r\u1ea5t l\u00e2u r\u1ed3i.</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 truy\u1ec1n ki\u1ebfp \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i k\u1ef3 World Cup l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 t\u1eebng \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh nh\u01b0 Brazil, \u0110\u1ee9c, T\u00e2y Ban Nha,\u2026 \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1edbm. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng l\u00e0m t\u0103ng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch c\u1ee7a Tam s\u01b0 \u1edf s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Croatia v\u00e0 xa h\u01a1n l\u00e0 Ph\u00e1p/B\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 ngang c\u01a1 v\u1edbi c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a HLV Gareth Southgate. V\u00e0 r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng, c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n Anh v\u00ec th\u1ebf c\u0169ng l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u0129 nhi\u00ean ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 v\u00ec th\u1ebf m\u00e0 t\u1ecf ra ch\u1ee7 quan b\u1edfi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 v\u00e0o t\u1edbi v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu. H\u1ecd c\u1ea7n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng v\u00e0 gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1i \u0111\u1ea7u l\u1ea1nh \u1edf nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u quan tr\u1ecdng s\u1eafp t\u1edbi. C\u00f3 nh\u01b0 v\u1eady th\u00ec chuy\u1ec7n\u00a0\u0110T Anh v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u vi\u1ec3n v\u00f4ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>\u2018G\u00e0 son\u2019 Harry Kane<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi 6 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, Harry Kane \u0111ang l\u00e0 ni\u1ec1m hy v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00e2n Anh tr\u00ean h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh chinh ph\u1ee5c chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap v\u00e0ng tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga h\u00e8 2018.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i, 6 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u00e0 Kane ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ec1u b\u1ecb ch\u00ea l\u00e0 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m penalty, nh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh, s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u00e2n s\u00fat Tottenham th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Harry Kane\" title=\"Harry Kane\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/6/world-cup-khong-chi-la-qua-bong.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Harry Kane l\u00e0 ni\u1ec1m hy v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh tr\u00ean h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh chinh ph\u1ee5c danh hi\u1ec7u World Cup</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">3 b\u00e0n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i th\u00ec c\u00f3 2 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1eadn th\u00e0nh trong tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n v\u1edbi Tunisia, c\u00f9ng 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng r\u1ea5t may m\u1eafn khi b\u00f3ng ch\u1ea1m ch\u00e2n Kane\u00a0t\u1eeb\u00a0c\u00fa s\u00fat xa c\u1ee7a Ruben Loftus-Cheek. N\u00f3i n\u00f4m na, Kane \u0111\u00e3 hay l\u1ea1i c\u00f2n... may. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u00edt th\u1edf b\u1ea7u kh\u00f4ng kh\u00ed \u1edf ng\u00e0y h\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u1ec9nh cao, Harry Kane \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o kh\u00e1c v\u00e0 bi\u1ebft \u0111\u00e2u anh s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u1edf c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft v\u00e0 chung k\u1ebft \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap \u0110T Anh tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh t\u00e2n v\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018.<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:\n115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/truoc-dai-chien-nguoi-croatia-lay-messi-ra-doa-tuyen-anh-421-190735.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/truoc-dai-chien-nguoi-croatia-lay-messi-ra-doa-tuyen-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/truoc-dai-chien-nguoi-croatia-lay-messi-ra-doa-tuyen-anh-421-190735.html\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn, ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia l\u1ea5y Messi ra d\u1ecda tuy\u1ec3n Anh</span><br>\r\nCroatia chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u1edbi Tam S\u01b0 \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft, v\u00e0 m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y HLV Dalic \u0111e d\u1ecda \u0110T Anh b\u1eb1ng tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 b\u1eaft ch\u1ebft Harry Kane.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hlv-croatia-de-cao-sterling-truoc-tran-ban-ket-gap-dt-anh-421-190780.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/7/hlv-croatia-de-cao-sterling-truoc-tran-ban-ket-gap-dt-anh.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hlv-croatia-de-cao-sterling-truoc-tran-ban-ket-gap-dt-anh-421-190780.html\">HLV Croatia \u0111\u1ec1 cao Sterling tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft g\u1eb7p \u0110T Anh</span><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00e1n k\u1ebft g\u1eb7p \u0110T Anh, HLV Croatia, Zlatko Dalic \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng khi n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 Raheem Sterling, ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Tam...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/mandzukic-canh-bao-dt-anh-truoc-dai-chien-469-190794.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/9/mandzukic-canh-bao-dt-anh-truoc-dai-chien.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/mandzukic-canh-bao-dt-anh-truoc-dai-chien-469-190794.html\">Mandzukic c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o \u0110T Anh tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn</span><br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Mario Mandzukic kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Croatia s\u1ebd chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 s\u1ee9c l\u1ef1c trong tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/goc-nhin-world-cup-2018/dt-anh-vao-ban-ket-world-cup-2018-khi-xu-angle-phu-bong-len-lich-su-466-190667.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/dt-anh-vao-ban-ket-world-cup-2018-khi-xu-angle-phu-bong-len-lich-su.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/goc-nhin-world-cup-2018/dt-anh-vao-ban-ket-world-cup-2018-khi-xu-angle-phu-bong-len-lich-su-466-190667.html\">\u0110T Anh v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018: Khi x\u1ee9 \u0102ng-l\u00ea ph\u1ee7 b\u00f3ng l\u00ean l\u1ecbch s\u1eed</span><br>\r\nMang b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 v\u1ec1 nh\u00e0 - \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 kh\u1ea9u hi\u1ec7u c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh khi ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018. Qu\u1ea3 th\u1ef1c gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u0103m nay \u0111ang ph\u1ee7...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<span style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</span></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1113","checkdouble":"190858"},{"date":"16:31 10/07","title":"Sterling \u0111ang c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup\u2026 tuy\u1ec7t hay","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/9/sterling-dang-co-mot-ky-world-cup-tuyet-hay.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Wayne Rooney v\u1eeba m\u1edbi c\u00f3 m\u00e0n ra m\u1eaft t\u1ea1i DC United. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, Rooney \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n Anh khi \u0111ang chinh chi\u1ebfn t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018.\r\n</h2><h2>Rooney ch\u00fac Anh v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a G\u00e3 Shrek thu\u1ed9c gi\u1ea3i MLS \u0111\u00e3 c\u1eaft b\u0103ng kh\u00e1nh th\u00e0nh SV\u0110 Audi Field, chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi. Tranh th\u1ee7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1eb7t nh\u1eefng c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi, c\u1ef1u ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Man United \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n Anh t\u1ea1i k\u1ef3 World Cup n\u00e0y, v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng t\u00edn hi\u1ec7u r\u1ea5t l\u1ea1c quan.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Kh\u00f4ng kh\u00ed l\u00fac n\u00e0y th\u1eadt tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi&rdquo; &ndash; Rooney cho bi\u1ebft. &ldquo;T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111ang mong ch\u1edd b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 nh\u00e0, c\u00f3 h\u00e0ng t\u1ec9 ng\u01b0\u1eddi theo d\u00f5i \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. Hy v\u1ecdng ch\u00fang ta c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft v\u00e0 ti\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;V\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u00e0 HLV Gareth Southgate, t\u00f4i ch\u00fac h\u1ecd may m\u1eafn. H\u1ecd \u0111ang khi\u1ebfn t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 ch\u00fang ta t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o. Hy v\u1ecdng to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfn th\u00eam m\u1ed9t b\u01b0\u1edbc n\u1eefa v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft, \u0111em c\u00fap v\u00e0ng v\u1ec1 nh\u00e0. T\u00f4i r\u1ea5t vui m\u1eebng khi ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3, v\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n tin t\u01b0\u1edfng c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Rooney \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n Anh trong ng\u00e0y kh\u00e1nh th\u00e0nh SV\u0110 c\u1ee7a DC United\" title=\"Rooney \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n Anh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/10/rooney-chuc-dan-em-vo-dich-world-cup-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Rooney \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n Anh trong ng\u00e0y kh\u00e1nh th\u00e0nh SV\u0110 c\u1ee7a DC United</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, c\u1ef1u \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng tuy\u1ec3n Anh c\u0169ng chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n ra m\u1eaft c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh t\u1ea1i DC United. Wayne Rooney cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i \u0111\u1ebfn ng\u00e0y x\u1ecf gi\u00e0y ra s\u00e2n, t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t mong ch\u1edd \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. V\u00e0o ng\u00e0y \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u00f4i c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 n\u00e0o qu\u00ean.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;T\u00f4i \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap CLB gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n v\u00e0 hy v\u1ecdng, ch\u00fang ta s\u1ebd v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi. T\u00f4i \u0111ang h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3, v\u00e0 \u0111em l\u1ea1i danh hi\u1ec7u cho SV\u0110 m\u1edbi khai tr\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u00e0y&rdquo;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0o \u0111\u00eam mai, \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Gareth Southgate s\u1ebd c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn chi\u1ebfn r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi Croatia. V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi Rooney \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n Anh, ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y \u0111ang r\u1ea5t mong ch\u1edd h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111em c\u00fap v\u00e0ng v\u1ec1 nh\u00e0.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/harry-kane-la-niem-cam-hung-cho-tre-em-beo-phi-421-190860.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/5/harry-kane-la-niem-cam-hung-cho-tre-em-beo-phi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/harry-kane-la-niem-cam-hung-cho-tre-em-beo-phi-421-190860.html\">Harry Kane l\u00e0 ni\u1ec1m c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng cho&hellip; tr\u1ebb em b\u00e9o ph\u00ec</span><br>\r\nT\u1ea1i n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00e2n \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111ang h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap v\u00e0ng. Nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i c\u01a1 s\u1edf chuy\u00ean v\u1ec1 dinh d\u01b0\u1ee1ng, h\u1ecd \u0111ang l\u1ea5y Kane l\u00e0 ni\u1ec1m c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng cho tr\u1ebb em...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/sterling-dang-co-mot-ky-world-cup-tuyet-hay-421-190859.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/9/sterling-dang-co-mot-ky-world-cup-tuyet-hay.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/sterling-dang-co-mot-ky-world-cup-tuyet-hay-421-190859.html\">Sterling \u0111ang c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup&hellip; tuy\u1ec7t hay</span><br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Eric Dier l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u01a1n b\u00e3o ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 v\u00f4 duy\u00ean c\u1ee7a anh tr\u01b0\u1edbc khung th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/4-ly-do-de-tin-dt-anh-se-vo-dich-world-cup-2018-421-190858.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/4-ly-do-de-tin-dt-anh-se-vo-dich-world-cup-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/4-ly-do-de-tin-dt-anh-se-vo-dich-world-cup-2018-421-190858.html\">4 l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 tin \u0110T Anh s\u1ebd v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018</span><br>\r\nN\u1eb1m \u1edf nh\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 m\u1ea1nh, \u0110T Anh \u0111ang ti\u1ebfn t\u1edbi s\u00e1t tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft h\u01a1n bao gi\u1edd h\u1ebft. V\u00e0 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 s\u1edf \u0111\u1ec3 tin r\u1eb1ng chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap v\u00e0ng World...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1112","checkdouble":"190859"},{"date":"16:31 10/07","title":"Harry Kane l\u00e0 ni\u1ec1m c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng cho\u2026 tr\u1ebb em b\u00e9o ph\u00ec","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/5/harry-kane-la-niem-cam-hung-cho-tre-em-beo-phi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>T\u1ea1i n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00e2n \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111ang h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap v\u00e0ng. Nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i c\u01a1 s\u1edf chuy\u00ean v\u1ec1 dinh d\u01b0\u1ee1ng, h\u1ecd \u0111ang l\u1ea5y Kane l\u00e0 ni\u1ec1m c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng cho tr\u1ebb em b\u00e9o ph\u00ec.\r\n</h2><h2>Harry Kane &ldquo;t\u1eeb v\u1ecbt h\u00f3a thi\u00ean nga&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00e2y gi\u1edd, ai c\u0169ng bi\u1ebft ch\u00e2n s\u00fat Tottenham l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. Trong n\u0103m d\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u1ecbch 2017, th\u00e0nh t\u00edch ghi b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a Harry Kane th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng ch\u00e2n s\u00fat kh\u00e9t ti\u1ebfng nh\u01b0 Cris Ronaldo, Leo Messi v\u00e0 Edinson Cavani.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede k\u1ef3 World Cup 2018 l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, Kane \u0111ang s\u1eafm vai tr\u00f2 th\u1ee7 l\u0129nh c\u1ee7a \u0110T qu\u1ed1c gia, v\u00e0 \u0111ang tr\u00e0n tr\u1ec1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i gi\u00e0nh danh hi\u1ec7u vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau ch\u00ednh c\u1ee7a anh v\u1eabn l\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0a Tam S\u01b0 gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean, c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y t\u1eebng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p th\u00ec kh\u00f4ng nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5. Theo \u0111\u00f3, anh t\u1eebng b\u1ecb t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u1edfi tuy\u1ec3n tr\u1ea1ch vi\u00ean Arsenal, b\u1edfi th\u00e2n h\u00ecnh b\u1ee5 b\u1eabm c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh khi c\u00f2n nh\u1ecf.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kane l\u00e0 ni\u1ec1m c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng cho tr\u1ebb em b\u00e9o ph\u00ec h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Kane l\u00e0 ni\u1ec1m c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng cho tr\u1ebb em b\u00e9o ph\u00ec h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/10/Kane-la-niem-cam-hung-cho-tre-em-beo-phi-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Kane l\u00e0 ni\u1ec1m c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng cho tr\u1ebb em b\u00e9o ph\u00ec</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;C\u1eadu \u1ea5y tr\u00f4ng nh\u01b0 b\u1ecb b\u00e9o ph\u00ec, tr\u00f4ng r\u1ea5t m\u1eadp m\u1ea1p, x\u01b0\u01a1ng to v\u00e0 kh\u00f3 v\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9ng. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do Arsenal t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i c\u1eadu \u1ea5y trong h\u1ecdc vi\u1ec7n. Kane kh\u00f4ng gi\u1ed1ng m\u1ed9t v\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean th\u1ec3 thao l\u1eafm, nh\u01b0ng b\u00e2y gi\u1edd t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u bi\u1ebft ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m&rdquo; &ndash; Liam Brady, tr\u01b0\u1edfng b\u1ed9 ph\u1eadn tuy\u1ec3n tr\u1ea1ch c\u1ee7a Arsenal chia s\u1ebb.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Harry Kane ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 ni\u1ec1m c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng cho nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ee9a tr\u1ebb b\u1ecb th\u1eeba c\u00e2n. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup, anh s\u1ebd l\u00e0 v\u00ed d\u1ee5 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi cho nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ee9a tr\u1ebb \u0111ang b\u1ecb ch\u1ecdc gh\u1eb9o v\u00ec b\u00e9o ph\u00ec, v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng c\u00e2u tr\u00eau \u0111\u00f9a ki\u1ec3u nh\u01b0 &ldquo;b\u1ecdn m\u1eadp tr\u00f4ng r\u1ea5t ngu ng\u1ed1c&rdquo;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3, r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 s\u1edf dinh d\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u0111ang l\u1ea5y Kane l\u00e0m h\u00ecnh m\u1eabu cho nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ee9a tr\u1ebb, b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh m\u1ed9t ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9 \u0103n u\u1ed1ng h\u1ee3p l\u00fd h\u01a1n. C\u00f2n v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng c\u00f4, c\u1eadu b\u00e9 \u0111ang b\u1ecb b\u1ea1n b\u00e8 nh\u1ea1o b\u00e1ng v\u00ec th\u1eeba c\u00e2n, ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111i theo con \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng tuy\u1ec3n Anh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/truoc-dai-chien-nguoi-croatia-lay-messi-ra-doa-tuyen-anh-421-190735.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/truoc-dai-chien-nguoi-croatia-lay-messi-ra-doa-tuyen-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/truoc-dai-chien-nguoi-croatia-lay-messi-ra-doa-tuyen-anh-421-190735.html\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn, ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia l\u1ea5y Messi ra d\u1ecda tuy\u1ec3n Anh</span><br>\r\nCroatia chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u1edbi Tam S\u01b0 \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft, v\u00e0 m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y HLV Dalic \u0111e d\u1ecda \u0110T Anh b\u1eb1ng tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 b\u1eaft ch\u1ebft Harry Kane.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/4-ly-do-de-tin-dt-anh-se-vo-dich-world-cup-2018-421-190858.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/4-ly-do-de-tin-dt-anh-se-vo-dich-world-cup-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/4-ly-do-de-tin-dt-anh-se-vo-dich-world-cup-2018-421-190858.html\">4 l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 tin \u0110T Anh s\u1ebd v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018</span><br>\r\nN\u1eb1m \u1edf nh\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 m\u1ea1nh, \u0110T Anh \u0111ang ti\u1ebfn t\u1edbi s\u00e1t tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft h\u01a1n bao gi\u1edd h\u1ebft. V\u00e0 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 s\u1edf \u0111\u1ec3 tin r\u1eb1ng chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap v\u00e0ng World...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1111","checkdouble":"190860"},{"date":"16:50 10/07","title":"Nh\u1eefng d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n s\u00f4i s\u1ee5c cho \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/10/nhung-du-doan-phap-vs-bi-va-nhan-dinh-soi-keo-phan-tich-ty-le-bi-vs-phap.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9 th\u1eadt kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ecdn ra ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng khi m\u00e0 c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i ph\u1ea3i n\u00f3i l\u00e0 c\u00e2n t\u00e0i c\u00e2n s\u1ee9c. \u1ede th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e2y, ch\u00fang ta ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u00e0n so t\u00e0i v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn v\u00e0 chuy\u1ec7n nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng l\u00e0 nh\u00ecn th\u1ea5y tr\u01b0\u1edbc.</h2><br>\r\n<h2>L\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- <strong>Nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi</strong><br>\r\nD\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1: Ph\u00e1p th\u1eafng 2-1<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u: Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9<br>\r\nTh\u1eddi gian: 1h ng\u00e0y 11/7<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m: S\u00e2n Saint-Petersburg<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTLCA c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn: Ph\u00e1p -0.91*0:1/4*0.86 B\u1ec9<br>\r\nTBT c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn: Nhi\u1ec1u -0.92*2 1/2*0.85 \u00cdt<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eefng d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9 v\u00e0 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh, soi k\u00e8o, t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 k\u00e8o h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eefng d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9 v\u00e0 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh, soi k\u00e8o, t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 k\u00e8o h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/10/nhung-du-doan-phap-vs-bi-va-nhan-dinh-soi-keo-phan-tich-ty-le-bi-vs-phap.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>D\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9 1h ng\u00e0y 1/7</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\n\u0110T Ph\u00e1p c\u00f3 h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng c\u1ef1c kh\u1ee7ng</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ea7u ti\u00ean ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eafc t\u1edbi b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i Kylian Mbappe v\u00e0 Antoine Griezmann. H\u1ecd l\u00e0 ngu\u1ed3n s\u1ed1ng c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p khi ghi t\u1edbi 6 trong t\u1ed5ng s\u1ed1 9 b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi l\u00fac n\u00e0y. T\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111i b\u00f3ng l\u1eaft l\u00e9o c\u1ee7a Mbappe v\u00e0 Griezmann gi\u00fap h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 san b\u1eb1ng b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKylian Mbappe ra m\u1eaft \u0110T Ph\u00e1p n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i v\u00e0 k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 19 tr\u1eadn, ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 7 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. C\u1ed9ng th\u00eam phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea1i PSG, th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 x\u1ee9 l\u1ee5c l\u0103ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi v\u00e0o \u0110TQG tham d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mbappe\" title=\"Mbappe\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/Daniel-van-Buyten-phat-bieu-ve-Kylian-Mbappe-hinh-anh.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Mbappe \u0111ang t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0 r\u1ea5t nhanh ch\u00f3ng, Mbappe \u0111\u00e3 x\u00f3a tan nh\u1eefng nghi ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 tu\u1ed5i t\u00e1c. Anh ghi b\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean cho Ph\u00e1p tr\u01b0\u1edbc Peru \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi tr\u1ebb nh\u1ea5t ghi b\u00e0n cho \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup. Ch\u01b0a d\u1eebng l\u1ea1i \u1edf \u0111\u00f3, Mbappe ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap tr\u01b0\u1edbc Argentina. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nK\u1ec3 t\u1eeb sau vua b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Pele, m\u1edbi l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tu\u1ed5i teen ghi 2 b\u00e0n 1 tr\u1eadn t\u1ea1i World Cup. T\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng, t\u1edbi nay Mbappe \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 3 pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng cho Ph\u00e1p tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga. Nh\u01b0ng ch\u01b0a h\u1ebft, t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng l\u1eeba b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a sao tr\u1ebb n\u00e0y lu\u00f4n khi\u1ebfn ph\u00eda b\u00ean kia ho\u1ea3ng lo\u1ea1n v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c so s\u00e1nh v\u1edbi Ronaldo &ndash; Ng\u01b0\u1eddi ngo\u00e0i h\u00e0nh tinh m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi. D\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u1ecf qua t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/mbappe-la-su-ket-hop-cua-ro-beo-henry-va-cristiano-421-190820.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/30/mbappe-la-su-ket-hop-cua-ro-beo-henry-va-cristiano.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/mbappe-la-su-ket-hop-cua-ro-beo-henry-va-cristiano-421-190820.html\">Mbappe l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a R\u00f4 b\u00e9o, Henry v\u00e0 Cristiano</span><br>\r\n<span>Daniel van Buyten ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Kylian Mbappe, c\u1ef1u sao tuy\u1ec3n B\u1ec9 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 pha tr\u1ed9n c\u1ee7a Ronaldo Brazil, Cristiano Ronaldo v\u00e0 Thierry...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1ec1 ph\u1ea7n Griezmann, th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf ch\u1ec9 ra anh \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i hy sinh nhi\u1ec1u cho tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p. \u0110\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p c\u1ee7a Griezmann v\u00e0 b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed ng\u01b0\u1eddi theo k\u00e8m s\u00e1t sao. V\u00ec v\u1eady, ng\u00f4i sao thu\u1ed9c bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf Atletico Madrid bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i l\u00f9i s\u00e2u t\u00ecm b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ec3 thu h\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi cho \u0111\u00e0n em Mbappe.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u00f9 v\u1eady, Griezmann c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 cho m\u00ecnh 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 b\u00e0n \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Uruguay. C\u1ed9ng v\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng l\u00e0m t\u01b0\u1eddng t\u1ed1t c\u1ee7a Giroud v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 ph\u00eda sau c\u1ee7a Paul Pogba, Ph\u00e1p c\u00f3 cho m\u00ecnh h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea7y s\u1ee9c n\u1eb7ng v\u00e0 r\u1ea5t bi\u1ebfn h\u00f3a.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u0169ng \u0111\u1eebng qu\u00ean r\u1eb1ng tr\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p v\u1eabn c\u00f2n nguy\u00ean m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t v\u0169 kh\u00ed l\u1ee3i h\u1ea1i. Nh\u1eefng Ousmane Dembele, Nabil Fekir, Thomas Lemar, Florian Thauvin&hellip; b\u1eb1ng nhi\u1ec1u c\u00e1ch v\u1eabn r\u1ea5t h\u1eefu \u00edch cho Les Bleus v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap h\u1ecd an t\u00e2m v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng xuy\u00ean th\u1ee7ng m\u00e0nh l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Varane ghi ban cho Phap\" title=\"Varane ghi ban cho Phap\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/7/4-diem-nhan-sau-chien-thang-20-cua-phap-truoc-uruguay.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Ph\u00e1p s\u1edf h\u1eefu nhi\u1ec1u ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng \u0111a d\u1ea1ng</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>\u0110T B\u1ec9 s\u1ee9t m\u1ebb h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u World Cup 2018, h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn ph\u1ea3i nhi\u1ec1u nghi ng\u1edd. Ngo\u1ea1i tr\u1eeb tr\u01b0\u1edbc Panama, t\u1edbi nay h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi \u1edf 4 trong 5 tr\u1eadn c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i. Trong \u0111\u00f3, Tunisia, Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh Brazil \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf 2 l\u1ea7n v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u1eb7t b\u00f3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00e1c trung v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a B\u1ec9 tr\u00ean l\u00fd thuy\u1ebft l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p, nh\u01b0ng hai c\u00e1nh c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd th\u00ec kh\u00f4ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng x\u1ee9ng. Tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y c\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e1ng lo h\u01a1n khi h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Thomas Meunier b\u1ecb treo gi\u00f2 do nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ed1 th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e1 thay h\u1ecd d\u00f9 l\u00e0 Nacer Chadli hay Dedryck Boyata c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 c\u00f2n tr\u00e1i s\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1eddng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"hau ve Meunier\" title=\"hau ve Meunier\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/10/hau-ve-Meunier.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Meunier b\u1ecb treo gi\u00f2 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i nhi\u1ec1u n\u1ed7i lo cho B\u1ec9</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 hai c\u00e1nh c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p xuy\u00ean ph\u00e1. Nh\u1eefng Griezmann v\u00e0 Mbappe \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i h\u1ea1i nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 ph\u00e2n t\u00edch. H\u1ecd c\u00f2n c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u1edbi t\u1eeb Lucas Hern\u00e1ndez v\u00e0 Benjamin Pavard \u0111\u1ea7y t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 \u1edf \u0111\u1eb1ng sau.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u00f3 c\u1ee7a B\u1ec9 kh\u00f4ng g\u00ec kh\u00e1c ngo\u00e0i l\u1ea5y c\u00f4ng b\u00f9 th\u1ee7. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 t\u1edbi 14 b\u00e0n ch\u1ec9 sau 5 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, t\u1ee9c trung b\u00ecnh g\u1ea7n 3 b\u00e0n/ tr\u1eadn. N\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 Ph\u00e1p c\u00f3 Griezmann v\u00e0 Mbappe th\u00ec B\u1ec9 c\u0169ng c\u00f3 Eden Hazard v\u00e0 De Bruyne l\u00e0m \u0111\u1ed1i tr\u1ecdng. V\u1edbi Lukaku th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed x\u00e9t v\u1ec1 3 m\u0169i c\u00f4ng ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c, B\u1ec9 c\u00f2n nh\u1ec9nh h\u01a1n Ph\u00e1p.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Bi lot vao ban ket World Cup\" title=\"Bi lot vao ban ket World Cup\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/9/Edwin-Van-der-Sar-du-doan-Bi-vo-dich-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">B\u1ec9 s\u1ebd l\u1ea5y c\u00f4ng b\u00f9 th\u1ee7</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>G\u00f3c soi k\u00e8o Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi s\u1ef1 quy t\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, b\u00e0n th\u1eafng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u hi\u1ec3n nhi\u00ean khi d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9. Vi\u1ec7c gi\u1edbi d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n ch\u00e2u \u00c1 ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0a m\u1ed1c 2,25 b\u00e0n cho cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t sai l\u1ea7m l\u1edbn. H\u1ecd \u0111ang ph\u1ea3i s\u1eeda sai t\u1eebng gi\u1edd t\u1eebng ph\u00fat v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c k\u00edch &ldquo;m\u1ed1c \u0111inh&rdquo; l\u00ean 2,5 b\u00e0n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 c\u1ea9n tr\u1ecdng t\u1edbi t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u00e0m lu\u1eadt. Nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd s\u1ebd c\u00f2n ph\u1ea3i \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh m\u1ecfi tay d\u1ef1a theo xu h\u01b0\u1edbng r\u00f5 m\u1ed3n m\u1ed9t nh\u01b0 hi\u1ec7n nay. M\u1ed1c 2 b\u00e0n ch\u1eb5n \u0111ang b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea9y xu\u1ed1ng cu\u1ed1i. N\u1ebfu \u0111\u00fang nh\u01b0 Bongda24h.vn d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n, m\u1ed1c 2,75 t\u1eeb gi\u1edd t\u1edbi s\u00e1t tr\u1eadn s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea9y l\u00ean ngang h\u00e0ng v\u1edbi m\u1ed1c 2,5 b\u00e0n hi\u1ec7n l\u00e0 tr\u1ecdng t\u00e2m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh tr\u00ean c\u00e0ng gi\u00fap nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi y\u00eau b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u1eb9p c\u00f3 th\u00eam ni\u1ec1m tin. Nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, \u0111\u1ea7y ni\u1ec1m vui l\u00e0 k\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n vi\u00ean m\u00e3n v\u1edbi ch\u00fang ta.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>L\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- <strong>Nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi</strong><br>\r\nD\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1: Ph\u00e1p th\u1eafng 2-1<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t kh\u00e1c</strong><br>\r\n- T\u1ed5ng s\u1ed1 qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn c\u1ee7a hai \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 9 (U 9 1/2)<br>\r\n- S\u1ed1 qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn c\u1ee7a B\u1ec9 t\u1eeb h\u00f2a t\u1edbi h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n- S\u1ed1 qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c hi\u1ec7p 1 c\u1ee7a B\u1ec9 t\u1eeb h\u00f2a t\u1edbi h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n- T\u1ed5ng s\u1ed1 th\u1ebb ph\u1ea1t c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn c\u1ee7a hai \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 4 (U 4)<br>\r\n- S\u1ed1 th\u1ebb ph\u1ea1t c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn c\u1ee7a B\u1ec9 t\u1eeb h\u00f2a t\u1edbi h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u1ea3i Ly (TTVN)<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1110","checkdouble":"190861"},{"date":"17:56 10/07","title":"Rooney ch\u00fac \u0111\u00e0n em v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/10/rooney-chuc-dan-em-vo-dich-world-cup-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Wayne Rooney v\u1eeba m\u1edbi c\u00f3 m\u00e0n ra m\u1eaft t\u1ea1i DC United. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, Rooney \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n Anh khi \u0111ang chinh chi\u1ebfn t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018.\r\n</h2><h2>Rooney ch\u00fac Anh v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a G\u00e3 Shrek thu\u1ed9c gi\u1ea3i MLS \u0111\u00e3 c\u1eaft b\u0103ng kh\u00e1nh th\u00e0nh SV\u0110 Audi Field, chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi. Tranh th\u1ee7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1eb7t nh\u1eefng c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi, c\u1ef1u ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Man United \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n Anh t\u1ea1i k\u1ef3 World Cup n\u00e0y, v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng t\u00edn hi\u1ec7u r\u1ea5t l\u1ea1c quan.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Kh\u00f4ng kh\u00ed l\u00fac n\u00e0y th\u1eadt tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi&rdquo; &ndash; Rooney cho bi\u1ebft. &ldquo;T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111ang mong ch\u1edd b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 nh\u00e0, c\u00f3 h\u00e0ng t\u1ec9 ng\u01b0\u1eddi theo d\u00f5i \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. Hy v\u1ecdng ch\u00fang ta c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft v\u00e0 ti\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;V\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u00e0 HLV Gareth Southgate, t\u00f4i ch\u00fac h\u1ecd may m\u1eafn. H\u1ecd \u0111ang khi\u1ebfn t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 ch\u00fang ta t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o. Hy v\u1ecdng to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfn th\u00eam m\u1ed9t b\u01b0\u1edbc n\u1eefa v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft, \u0111em c\u00fap v\u00e0ng v\u1ec1 nh\u00e0. T\u00f4i r\u1ea5t vui m\u1eebng khi ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3, v\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n tin t\u01b0\u1edfng c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Rooney \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n Anh trong ng\u00e0y kh\u00e1nh th\u00e0nh SV\u0110 c\u1ee7a DC United\" title=\"Rooney \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n Anh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/10/rooney-chuc-dan-em-vo-dich-world-cup-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Rooney \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n Anh trong ng\u00e0y kh\u00e1nh th\u00e0nh SV\u0110 c\u1ee7a DC United</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, c\u1ef1u \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng tuy\u1ec3n Anh c\u0169ng chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n ra m\u1eaft c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh t\u1ea1i DC United. Wayne Rooney cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i \u0111\u1ebfn ng\u00e0y x\u1ecf gi\u00e0y ra s\u00e2n, t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t mong ch\u1edd \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. V\u00e0o ng\u00e0y \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u00f4i c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 n\u00e0o qu\u00ean.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;T\u00f4i \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap CLB gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n v\u00e0 hy v\u1ecdng, ch\u00fang ta s\u1ebd v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi. T\u00f4i \u0111ang h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3, v\u00e0 \u0111em l\u1ea1i danh hi\u1ec7u cho SV\u0110 m\u1edbi khai tr\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u00e0y&rdquo;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0o \u0111\u00eam mai, \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Gareth Southgate s\u1ebd c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn chi\u1ebfn r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi Croatia. V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi Rooney \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n Anh, ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y \u0111ang r\u1ea5t mong ch\u1edd h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111em c\u00fap v\u00e0ng v\u1ec1 nh\u00e0.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/harry-kane-la-niem-cam-hung-cho-tre-em-beo-phi-421-190860.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/5/harry-kane-la-niem-cam-hung-cho-tre-em-beo-phi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/harry-kane-la-niem-cam-hung-cho-tre-em-beo-phi-421-190860.html\">Harry Kane l\u00e0 ni\u1ec1m c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng cho&hellip; tr\u1ebb em b\u00e9o ph\u00ec</span><br>\r\nT\u1ea1i n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00e2n \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111ang h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap v\u00e0ng. Nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i c\u01a1 s\u1edf chuy\u00ean v\u1ec1 dinh d\u01b0\u1ee1ng, h\u1ecd \u0111ang l\u1ea5y Kane l\u00e0 ni\u1ec1m c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng cho tr\u1ebb em...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/sterling-dang-co-mot-ky-world-cup-tuyet-hay-421-190859.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/9/sterling-dang-co-mot-ky-world-cup-tuyet-hay.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/sterling-dang-co-mot-ky-world-cup-tuyet-hay-421-190859.html\">Sterling \u0111ang c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup&hellip; tuy\u1ec7t hay</span><br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Eric Dier l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u01a1n b\u00e3o ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 v\u00f4 duy\u00ean c\u1ee7a anh tr\u01b0\u1edbc khung th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/4-ly-do-de-tin-dt-anh-se-vo-dich-world-cup-2018-421-190858.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/4-ly-do-de-tin-dt-anh-se-vo-dich-world-cup-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/4-ly-do-de-tin-dt-anh-se-vo-dich-world-cup-2018-421-190858.html\">4 l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 tin \u0110T Anh s\u1ebd v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018</span><br>\r\nN\u1eb1m \u1edf nh\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 m\u1ea1nh, \u0110T Anh \u0111ang ti\u1ebfn t\u1edbi s\u00e1t tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft h\u01a1n bao gi\u1edd h\u1ebft. V\u00e0 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 s\u1edf \u0111\u1ec3 tin r\u1eb1ng chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap v\u00e0ng World...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1109","checkdouble":"190862"},{"date":"17:29 10/07","title":"\u0110\u00e2y! Nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n Croatia v\u00e0o t\u1edbi b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/10/day-nguyen-nhan-croatia-vao-ban-ket-world-cup-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Croatia v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 g\u1eb7p \u0110T Anh tr\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1ef1 s\u1eedng s\u1ed1t c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi. \u0110\u1ebfn c\u1ef1u danh th\u1ee7 Filip Tapalovic c\u0169ng ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c n\u00e0y, nh\u01b0ng \u00f4ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh tinh th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap h\u1ecd l\u00e0m n\u00ean k\u1ef3 t\u00edch.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCroatia v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t Anh \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 t\u1ea1i Moscow \u0111\u00eam mai (11/7). V\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea7u t\u00e0u l\u00e0 Luka Modric v\u00e0 Ivan Rakitic, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u00e1o caro x\u1ee9ng danh l\u00e0 \u201cng\u1ef1a \u00f4\u201d t\u1ea1i b\u00e1n k\u1ebft gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nFilip Tapalovic, m\u1ed9t c\u1ef1u tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Croatia cho bi\u1ebft s\u1ef1 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p nhi\u1ec1u y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 \u0111\u00e3 mang t\u1edbi th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng cho h\u1ecd. Sau 20 n\u0103m, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y l\u1ea1i l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft c\u1ee7a c\u00fap th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. \u201cT\u00f4i r\u1ea5t ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean. H\u1ecd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 m\u1ea1nh, nh\u01b0ng trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9 \u0111\u00e3 m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i l\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 v\u1eady m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng\u201d, tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd HLV c\u1ee7a CLB Adelaide United (Australia) n\u00f3i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n Croatia v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 g\u1eb7p \u0110T Anh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n Croatia v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 g\u1eb7p \u0110T Anh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/10/day-nguyen-nhan-croatia-vao-ban-ket-world-cup-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>\u0110T\u00a0Croatia v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i ngh\u0129 h\u1ecd c\u00f3 tinh th\u1ea7n tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi khi thi \u0111\u1ea5u. M\u00e0 tinh th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i l\u1ea1i r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng cho m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn. H\u1ecd r\u1ea5t k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt, c\u00f3 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c, c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 t\u1ed1t v\u1edbi Rakitic v\u00e0 Modric. C\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1eebng gi\u00e0nh c\u00e1c danh hi\u1ec7u trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9 c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi CLB c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 \u1edf Croatia v\u1edbi Dinamo Zagreb m\u00e0 c\u00f2n \u1edf b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i t\u1ea1i Ph\u00e1p, Italia, T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u00e0 c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kinh nghi\u1ec7m.\u201d<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>T\u1ef1 tin s\u1ebd v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 k\u1ebf ti\u1ebfp c\u1ee7a Croatia l\u00e0 \u0110T Anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n. Nh\u01b0ng Tapalovic tin r\u1eb1ng v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 h\u01b0ng ph\u1ea5n s\u1eb5n c\u00f3, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng qu\u00ea h\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00ecnh s\u1ebd l\u00e0m n\u00ean b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd. \u201c\u0110\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd. C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 World Cup cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng cho m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i ng\u01b0\u1eddi nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u00fac h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ea1t t\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9 ch\u00edn.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cNgo\u00e0i ra, Croatia c\u00f3 may m\u1eafn, \u0111i\u1ec1u xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n \u1edf m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 h\u1ecd x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00e0 hy v\u1ecdng h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft.\u201d<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 \u0110T Croatia tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/dt-croatia-mat-hlv-vi-khieu-khich-chu-nha-nga-421-190822.html\">\u0110T Croatia m\u1ea5t HLV v\u00ec khi\u00eau kh\u00edch ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Nga</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/modric-la-cau-thu-xuat-sac-nhat-world-cup-2018-421-190810.html\">Modric l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/mandzukic-canh-bao-dt-anh-truoc-dai-chien-469-190794.html\">Mandzukic c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o \u0110T Anh tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hlv-croatia-de-cao-sterling-truoc-tran-ban-ket-gap-dt-anh-421-190780.html\">HLV Croatia \u0111\u1ec1 cao Sterling tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft g\u1eb7p \u0110T Anh</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hlv-dalic-phat-bieu-ve-rakitic-421-190779.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng penalty c\u1ee7a Croatia \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khen h\u1ebft l\u1eddi</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1108","checkdouble":"190863"},{"date":"17:09 10/07","title":"Nh\u1eefng cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u n\u00f3ng b\u1ecfng \u1edf \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/10/nhung-cuoc-doi-dau-nong-bong-o-dai-chien-phap-vs-bi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ph\u00e1p v\u00e0 B\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga, cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ecd s\u1ee9c gi\u1eefa h\u1ecd s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng v\u00e0 quy\u1ebft li\u1ec7t. C\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua nh\u1eefng cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u n\u00f3ng b\u1ecfng \u1edf \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9 v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">N'Golo Kante vs Kevin de Bruyne</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Brazil, Kevin de Bruyne b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 trung phong c\u1eafm trong s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 4-3-3. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 ch\u01a1i \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed cao nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng, song ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Man City th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean di chuy\u1ec3n r\u1ea5t r\u1ed9ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eefng cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9 v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eefng cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9 v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/10/Nhung-cuoc-doi-dau-Phap-vs-Bi-vong-ban-ket-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>N'Golo Kante vs Kevin de Bruyne</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ed3 nhi\u1ec7t cho th\u1ea5y t\u1ea7m ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng ch\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu c\u1ee7a De Bruyne \u1edf khu v\u1ef1c gi\u1eefa s\u00e2n, anh ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng ch\u01a1i th\u1ea5p qua \u0111\u00f3 t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n cho Lukaku v\u00e0 Hazard x\u00e2m nh\u1eadp v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng. De Bruyne \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 l\u00e0m b\u00f3ng, k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i gi\u1eefa h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 v\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nN'Golo Kante ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c giao nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 phong t\u1ecfa s\u1ef1 nguy hi\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a ng\u00f2i n\u1ed5 De Bruyne, ngay khi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i nh\u1eadn b\u00f3ng ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Chelsea s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i g\u00e2y s\u1ee9c \u00e9p qua \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a B\u1ec9 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u th\u1eddi gian v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng gian \u0111\u1ec3 x\u1eed l\u00fd b\u00f3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Brazil, kh\u00f4ng m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 n\u00e0o c\u1ee7a Selecao c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 phong t\u1ecfa kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng r\u1ea5t r\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a De Bruyne. Nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c sung m\u00e3n c\u00f9ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111eo b\u00e1m d\u1ebbo dai, Kante h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1991 g\u1eb7p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nDe Bruyne v\u00e0 Kante \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh khi Man City \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 Chelsea, hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 hi\u1ec3u bi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 nhau. Cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ecd s\u1ee9c gi\u1eefa h\u1ecd r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Raphael Varane vs Eden Hazard</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Eden Hazard l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 s\u1ed1 l\u1ea7n ch\u1ea1m b\u00f3ng trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m Brazil nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft. D\u00f9 ch\u01a1i \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i nh\u01b0ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kho\u00e1c \u00e1o s\u1ed1 10 th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9t ph\u00e1 v\u00e0o trung l\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m ho\u1eb7c ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Raphael Varane vs Eden Hazard\" title=\"Raphael Varane vs Eden Hazard\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/10/varane.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Raphael Varane vs Eden Hazard</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Hazard khi\u1ebfn Fagner m\u1ec7t nho\u00e0i, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed anh c\u00f2n c\u00f3 10 l\u1ea7n qua ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. \u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Ph\u00e1p, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt, t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng qua ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Hazard s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 Les Bleus g\u1eb7p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nRaphael Varane v\u1edbi kinh nghi\u1ec7m, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00e1n \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ed1t c\u00f9ng s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh trong nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng tranh ch\u1ea5p s\u1ebd c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 \u00e1p s\u00e1t khi Hazard \u0111i b\u00f3ng t\u1eeb bi\u00ean v\u00e0o trung l\u1ed9.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nVarane t\u1ec9nh t\u00e1o h\u01a1n Umtiti trong nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng v\u00e0o b\u00f3ng, ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1993 c\u0169ng c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ch\u1ecbu \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ee9c \u00e9p l\u1edbn h\u01a1n do tham gia r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a Real \u1edf \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u00e2u \u00c2u. B\u1edfi v\u1eady, Varane \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf t\u1ed1i \u0111a s\u1ef1 nguy hi\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao 27 tu\u1ed5i b\u00ean ph\u00eda \u0110T B\u1ec9.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Antoine Griezmann vs Nacer Chadli</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng HLV Didier Deschamps s\u1ebd s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 4-2-3-1 \u1edf tr\u1eadn <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-phap-vs-bi-1h-ngay-117-dinh-cao-hoi-tu-o-st-petersburg-421-190815.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9 </span>v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018, Giroud v\u1eabn s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1 cao nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng. Ph\u00eda sau l\u00e0 b\u1ed9 ba Matuidi, Griezmann v\u00e0 Mbappe.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Griezmann mo ty so tren cham 11m\" title=\"Griezmann m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m 11m\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/30/griezmann-phap-xung-dang-gianh-ve-vao-tu-ket.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Griezmann s\u1ebd khai th\u00e1c v\u00e0o v\u1ecb tr\u00ed do Chadli \u0111\u1ea3m nhi\u1ec7m</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 n\u00e0y, Griezmann \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed h\u1ed9 c\u00f4ng nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 th\u00f3i quen di chuy\u1ec3n sang c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i. T\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y anh s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 Nacer Chadli, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1 thay v\u1ecb tr\u00ed do Thomas Meunier b\u1ecb treo gi\u00f2 b\u1edfi th\u1ebb ph\u1ea1t.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNacer Chadli kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh thu\u1ea7n t\u00fay, \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 Griezmann khai th\u00e1c v\u00e0o v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 &ldquo;t\u1eed huy\u1ec7t&rdquo; n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a B\u1ec9.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCh\u1eafc ch\u1eafn Ph\u00e1p s\u1ebd khai th\u00e1c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0o v\u1ecb tr\u00ed m\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o West Brom \u0111\u1ea3m nhi\u1ec7m. T\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9, k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng qua ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Griezmann h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn Chadli c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1ec7t nho\u00e0i.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Didier Deschamps vs Roberto Martinez</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cu\u1ed9c chi\u1ebfn tr\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ea1o gi\u1eefa Didier Deschamps v\u00e0 Roberto Martinez s\u1ebd quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ebfn c\u1ee5c di\u1ec7n tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. C\u1ea3 2 HLV \u0111\u1ec1u g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Didier Deschamps vs Roberto Martinez\" title=\"Didier Deschamps vs Roberto Martinez\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/10/hlv.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Didier Deschamps vs Roberto Martinez</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nDeschamps gi\u00fap Ph\u00e1p duy tr\u00ec m\u1ed9t th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn t\u1ed1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc Argentina v\u00e0 Uruguay, nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng c\u0169ng t\u1ecf ra r\u1ea5t h\u1ee3p l\u00fd. Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n 49 tu\u1ed5i \u0111ang duy tr\u00ec s\u1ef1 h\u01b0ng ph\u1ea5n r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn cho c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nB\u00ean kia chi\u1ebfn tuy\u1ebfn, Roberto Martinez \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Tite trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Brazil. Nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i t\u1eeb c\u1ef1u HLV Everton khi\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng nghi\u1ec7p b\u00ean kia chi\u1ebfn tuy\u1ebfn kh\u00f4ng k\u1ecbp tr\u1edf tay. HLV Tite sau \u0111\u00f3 th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn B\u1ec9 x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9, th\u00e0nh b\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 \u1edf chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt m\u00e0 c\u00f2n \u1edf ni\u1ec1m tin m\u00e0 Didier Deschamps v\u00e0 Roberto Martinez t\u1ea1o ra cho c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2, c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi c\u1ee5c di\u1ec7n tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng ch\u1ec9 thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 HLV \u0111\u01b0a ra nh\u1eefng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u00e1ng su\u1ed1t v\u00e0 t\u1ecf ra b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh h\u01a1n \u1edf nh\u1eefng th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1107","checkdouble":"190864"},{"date":"17:40 10/07","title":"Eden Hazard t\u1edbi La Liga nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i Real?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/7/eden-hazard-toi-la-liga-nhung-khong-phai-real.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Barca mu\u1ed1n mua Eden Hazard, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 100 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t Real Madrid trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Barca gia nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh Hazard</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Eden Hazard l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ec1 t\u00e0i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e1o ch\u00ed khai th\u00e1c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn. Real quan t\u00e2m Hazard, ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Perez mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Barca mu\u1ed1n mua Eden Hazard v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 100 tri\u1ec7u euro \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Barca mu\u1ed1n mua Eden Hazard v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 100 tri\u1ec7u euro \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/10/Barca-muon-mua-Eden-Hazard-voi-gia-100-trieu-euro-o-He-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Barca mu\u1ed1n mua Eden Hazard</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Real mua Hazard b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd tr\u1edf n\u00ean kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n khi h\u1ecd c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. Theo Sport c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha, Barca mu\u1ed1n mua Eden Hazard, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi \u0111\u1eadm mua ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBarca v\u1eeba nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Antoine Griezmann t\u1eeb Atletico Madrid, h\u1ecd nh\u1eafm Hazard thay c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p. \u0110\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t Real Madrid trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ea9y nhanh t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBarca s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n m\u00e0 Chelsea y\u00eau c\u1ea7u, theo \u0111\u00f3 h\u1ecd s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi t\u1edbi 100 tri\u1ec7u euro cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 The Sun kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chelsea-tu-choi-loi-de-nghi-dau-tien-cua-real-cho-hazard-172-190852.html\" target=\"_blank\">Chelsea t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n Hazard cho Real</span> v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 60 tri\u1ec7u euro.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Barca c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Hazard</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng gi\u1eefa Hazard v\u1edbi Chelsea ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ebfn n\u0103m 2020, The Blues \u0111\u00e3 nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n mu\u1ed1n gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1991 nh\u01b0ng anh \u0111\u1ec1u t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh mu\u1ed1n ki\u1ec3m ch\u1ee9ng tham v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a Chelsea tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u00f3 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi hay kh\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Eden Hazard Chelsea\" title=\"Eden Hazard Chelsea\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/31/hazard-nen-tu-choi-real-de-tro-thanh-huyen-thoai-cua-chelsea.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u00e1n Eden Hazard \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Roman Abramovich \u0111ang t\u1ee9c gi\u1eadn v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i \u201cc\u00e2u gi\u1edd\u201d t\u1eeb ph\u00eda Hazard, Mirror kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u00f4ng n\u00e0y s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1991 n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb h\u1ee3p l\u00fd.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nReal \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n quan t\u00e2m Hazard t\u1eeb kh\u00e1 l\u00e2u, nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i quy\u1ebft li\u1ec7t trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. N\u1ebfu Barca \u0111\u1ea9y nhanh ti\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n, \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n m\u00e0 Chelsea y\u00eau c\u1ea7u v\u00e0 tr\u1ea3 l\u01b0\u01a1ng r\u1ea5t cao cho Hazard, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ecd c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHazard hi\u1ec7n v\u1eabn \u0111ang c\u00f9ng \u0110T B\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf World Cup 2018, ng\u00f4i sao 27 tu\u1ed5i m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u1ecdi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1u mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u00e1 cho Real.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNg\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1991 \u01b0u ti\u00ean t\u1edbi Bernabeu n\u1ebfu r\u1eddiChelsea, nh\u01b0ng trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Los Blancos kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i th\u00e1i quy\u1ebft li\u1ec7t th\u00ec anh ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ebfn chuy\u1ec7n t\u1edbi Barca.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1106","checkdouble":"190865"},{"date":"17:32 10/07","title":"4 c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/10/4-cai-ten-dang-chu-y-o-ban-ket-world-cup-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>World Cup 2018 \u0111ang d\u1ea7n b\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1ed3i k\u1ebft. Ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 4 c\u00e1i t\u00ean tr\u1ee5 l\u1ea1i l\u00fac n\u00e0y B\u1ec9, Ph\u00e1p, Croatia v\u00e0 Anh. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 4 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u1eefng si\u00eau sao h\u1ea1ng n\u1eb7ng. V\u00e0 d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a 4 \u0111\u1ed9i g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft.</h2><h2>Luka Modric &ndash; Croatia\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"4 c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"4 c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/10/4-cai-ten-dang-chu-y-o-ban-ket-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Modric l\u00e0 ni\u1ec1m hy v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a Croatia tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Luka Modric ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Croatia v\u00e0o th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y. \u0110\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a Vatreni \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i 485 ph\u00fat \u1edf World Cup 2018, nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i n\u00e0o. Anh ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 &ldquo;nh\u1ea1c tr\u01b0\u1edfng&rdquo; c\u1ee7a Croatia v\u00e0 li\u00ean t\u1ee5c t\u1ea1o ra \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u0103m nay.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nModric \u0111\u00e3 ghi 2 b\u00e0n v\u00e0 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o 1 l\u1ea7n cho \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00fac n\u00e0y. Nh\u1edd v\u1eady, anh \u0111ang l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u danh s\u00e1ch ghi b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a Croatia.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nModric s\u1ebd l\u00e0 nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 quan tr\u1ecdng khi Croatia \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Anh \u1edf tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft th\u1ee9 hai c\u1ee7a <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018-c421-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">World Cup 2018</span>. Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ecdc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh Croatia c\u00f3 b\u1ecb l\u00e9p v\u1ebf tr\u01b0\u1edbc Tam S\u01b0 \u1edf khu trung tuy\u1ebfn hay kh\u00f4ng. N\u1ebfu Modric c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ec7, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng cao Croatia s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i h\u1ee9ng ch\u1ecbu h\u1eadu qu\u1ea3 v\u00e0 l\u00ean m\u00e1y bay v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc sau v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<h2>Romelu Lukaku &ndash; B\u1ec9\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lukaku\" title=\"Lukaku\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/10/2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Lukaku l\u00e0 ch\u00e2n s\u00fat t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a B\u1ec9 l\u00fac n\u00e0y</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Lukaku \u0111\u00e3 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 27 b\u00e0n cho Man United tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i. \u0110\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch ghi b\u00e0n t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p ch\u00e2n s\u00fat 25 tu\u1ed5i. V\u00e0 may m\u1eafn cho \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n B\u1ec9 l\u00e0 Lukaku \u0111\u00e3 \u0111em phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ec9nh cao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh t\u1edbi s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i World Cup.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0o l\u00fac n\u00e0y, Lukaku \u0111\u00e3 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 4 b\u00e0n v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p 1 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o. Anh \u0111ang l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ghi nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a &ldquo;Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf&rdquo; v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 2 trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh danh hi\u1ec7u Vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi World Cup sau Harry Kane. Lukaku li\u00ean k\u1ebft r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t v\u1edbi b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 De Bruyne v\u00e0 Hazard \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean c\u01a1n \u00e1c m\u1ed9ng cho h\u1ea7u h\u1ebft m\u1ecdi h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 anh ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u \u1edf gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p, Lukaku s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i t\u1ea1o ra m\u1ed9t m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n ch\u00f3i s\u00e1ng n\u1eefa n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 mu\u1ed1n gi\u00fap B\u1ec9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp. M\u1ed9t v\u00e0i kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc ma thu\u1eadt l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00e0 Lukaku c\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ec3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i c\u1ee5c di\u1ec7n tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. B\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng hay kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0o phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Lukaku \u1edf tr\u1eadn t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<h2>Harry Kane &ndash; Anh\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kane\" title=\"Kane\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/10/172656-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Kane \u0111ang d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u danh s\u00e1ch ghi b\u00e0n \u1edf World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a Tam S\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 l\u0129nh xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y. Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a Tottenham \u0111\u00e3 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 6 b\u00e0n trong khi t\u1ed5ng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i m\u1edbi ch\u1ea1m con s\u1ed1 5.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh ch\u01b0a g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o kh\u00f3 cho t\u1edbi l\u00fac n\u00e0y. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Croatia s\u1ebd l\u00e0 th\u1eed th\u00e1ch kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n h\u01a1n \u0111\u00f4i ch\u00fat v\u1edbi \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Southgate. V\u00e0 Kane ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ph\u1ea3i g\u00e1nh tr\u00ean vai s\u1ef1 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 l\u1edbn \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong v\u00e0i n\u0103m g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, Kane \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u00f3 r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u00e1p l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng. V\u00e0 s\u1ef1 b\u00ecnh t\u0129nh c\u1ee7a anh l\u00e0 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 quan tr\u1ecdng n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Croatia. Ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n Kane ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 1 ho\u1eb7c 2 b\u00e0n, s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t coi nh\u01b0 qu\u00e1 r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng v\u00e0 Anh s\u1ebd th\u1eb3ng ti\u1ebfn v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft.</div>\r\n<h2>Kylian Mbappe &ndash; Ph\u00e1p\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mbappe\" title=\"Mbappe\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/Daniel-van-Buyten-phat-bieu-ve-Kylian-Mbappe-hinh-anh.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Mbappe li\u00ean t\u1ee5c t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u0103m nay</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sao tr\u1ebb Mbappe \u0111\u00e3 ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 19 tu\u1ed5i s\u1edf h\u1eefu t\u00e0i n\u0103ng thi\u00ean b\u1ea9m v\u00e0 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tu\u1ed5i teen \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 2 b\u00e0n trong m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf World Cup t\u1eeb th\u1eddi Pele.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMbappe l\u00e0 h\u1ea1t nh\u00e2n trong th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y. T\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Mbappe \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea3 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi ph\u1ea3i s\u1eefng s\u1edd. Mbappe \u0111ang l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nguy hi\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi v\u00e0o l\u00fac n\u00e0y. Anh g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o ra \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t n\u1ebfu c\u00f3 b\u00f3ng trong ch\u00e2n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMbappe \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i 354 ph\u00fat v\u00e0 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. Anh l\u00e0 ch\u00e2n s\u00fat t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh si\u00eau sao Antoine Griezmann. \u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00eam nay, Mbappe nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng b\u00ean h\u00e0nh lang ph\u1ea3i. V\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng b\u1ee9t t\u1ed1c c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u00f3 l\u1ebd s\u1ebd mang \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat gi\u00e2y kh\u00f3 th\u1edf cho h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ch\u1eadm ch\u1ea1p c\u1ee7a &ldquo;Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf&rdquo;.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMbappe s\u1edf h\u1eefu kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 th\u1eadt kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u0103n anh ghi b\u00e0n n\u1ebfu ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n h\u1eadu v\u1ec7. C\u0169ng nh\u1edd v\u1eady, Mbappe thu h\u00fat \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng m\u1edf ra nh\u1eefng kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng cho Giroud c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 Griezmann t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/video-nhan-dinh-phap-vs-bi-phan-tich-chien-thuat-tran-ban-ket-world-cup-2018-421-190856.html\">Video: Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9 - ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/3-ly-do-de-tin-bi-se-danh-bai-phap-o-ban-ket-world-cup-421-190842.html\">3 l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 tin B\u1ec9 s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Ph\u00e1p \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1105","checkdouble":"190868"},{"date":"10:12 10/07","title":"Ashley Young c\u00f3 v\u00e0i l\u1eddi mu\u1ed1n g\u1eedi \u0111\u1ebfn \u0110T Anh","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/10/su-tro-lai-ruc-ro-cua-binh-doan-quy-do.PNG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ashley Young ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Anh, ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o MU kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Tam s\u01b0 v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 g\u00ec c\u1ea3, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i t\u1eadp trung ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Croatia.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ashley Young khuy\u00ean \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i gi\u1eef \u0111\u00f4i ch\u00e2n tr\u00ean m\u1eb7t \u0111\u1ea5t</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nAnh \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t \u1edf World Cup 2018, h\u1ecd \u0111ang \u0111i \u0111i nh\u1eefng b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u1eefng ch\u1eafc \u0111\u1ebfn ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch. \u1ede b\u00e1n k\u1ebft, Tam s\u01b0 s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 Croatia. X\u00e9t v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh S\u01b0 t\u1eed Anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ashley Young ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Anh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ashley Young ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Anh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/10/su-tro-lai-ruc-ro-cua-binh-doan-quy-do.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ashley Young n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Anh vs Croatia</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u1ebfu ch\u01a1i \u0111\u00fang th\u1ef1c l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, Anh ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Croatia \u0111\u1ec3 v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft g\u1eb7p B\u1ec9 ho\u1eb7c Ph\u00e1p. Sau r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m th\u00ec Tam s\u01b0 m\u1edbi l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i l\u00ean ng\u00f4i \u1edf m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, Ashley Young ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Anh, ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o MU kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Tam s\u01b0 v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 g\u00ec c\u1ea3, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i t\u1eadp trung ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Croatia.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\"Th\u1eadt tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi khi c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 g\u00ec trong tay c\u1ea3, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft m\u00e0 th\u00f4i. V\u1eabn c\u00f2n m\u1ed9t ch\u1eb7ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng r\u1ea5t d\u00e0i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111i \u0111\u1ebfn ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1eadp trung \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 \u0111\u00fang th\u1ef1c l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0a ra nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ea5u ph\u00e1p th\u00edch h\u1ee3p. T\u00f4i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nhi\u1ec1u tu\u1ed5i nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Anh, t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean t\u00f4i c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng kinh nghi\u1ec7m thi \u0111\u1ea5u trong nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd chia s\u1ebb \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 cho nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb h\u01a1n\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Ashley Young tin Anh c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf h\u01a1n Croatia</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Anh \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i nh\u00e0n nh\u00e3 trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-0, trong khi \u0111\u00f3 Croatia ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1 11m m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Nga.\u00a0<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Preview Croatia vs Anh\" title=\"Preview Croatia vs Anh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/10/Anh-vs-Croatia.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Young tin Anh c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf h\u01a1n Croatia v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 2 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp h\u1ecd ph\u1ea3i nh\u1edd \u0111\u1ebfn lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u00e1 lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7, tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110an M\u1ea1ch. Ashley Young\u00a0th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn Anh c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf h\u01a1n Croatia v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i ngh\u0129 v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t th\u1ec3 ch\u1ea5t Anh \u0111ang c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf, Croatia ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1 120 ph\u00fat trong c\u1ea3 2 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea7n t\u1edbi lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u00e1 11m m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd. Croatia \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb b\u00e0o m\u00f2n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c, nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p ch\u1ee7 quan\u201d.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/eric-dier-chi-ra-2-cau-thu-nguy-hiem-nhat-cua-croatia-421-190830.html\" target=\"_blank\">Eric Dier c\u0169ng ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Anh</span>, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Spurs khuy\u00ean Tam s\u01b0 c\u1ea3nh gi\u00e1c v\u1edbi b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i Rakitic v\u00e0 Modric c\u1ee7a Croatia.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1104","checkdouble":"190832"},{"date":"10:58 10/07","title":"Lovren \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1o th\u00f9 Harry Kane","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/10/lov.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018, trung v\u1ec7 Dejan Lovren th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c Harry Kane v\u00e0 \u0111ang h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.\r\n</h2><h2>Lovren s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua n\u1ed7i \u00e1m \u1ea3nh<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1eafp t\u1edbi, Croatia s\u1ebd ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n \u0110T Anh t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft cho m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfc v\u00e9 \u0111i \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng. Hi\u1ec7n nay, Tam S\u01b0 \u0111ang s\u1edf h\u1eefu c\u00e1i t\u00ean d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u danh s\u00e1ch ghi b\u00e0n \u1edf k\u1ef3 World Cup l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y &ndash; Harry Kane. B\u1edfi v\u1eady n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u00e1o s\u1ecdc ca-ro c\u1ea7n ch\u1eb7n \u0111\u1ee9ng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Tottenham.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hay n\u00f3i c\u00e1ch kh\u00e1c, \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 cu\u1ed9c chi\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 Croatia, v\u1edbi trung v\u1ec7 Dejan Lovren n\u1eafm tr\u1ecdng tr\u00e1ch n\u1eb7ng n\u1ec1. D\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 k\u1ebft th\u00fac m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1edbi v\u1ecb th\u1ebf \u00c1 qu\u00e2n Champions League, nh\u01b0ng Lovren t\u1eebng b\u1ecb Harry Kane s\u1ec9 nh\u1ee5c trong l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, khi Liverpool thua th\u1ea3m Tottenham 1-4.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lovren th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c Harry Kane\" title=\"Lovren th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c Harry Kane\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/10/lov.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Lovren th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c Harry Kane</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 The Kop cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;Kane l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t Premier League. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng v\u1edbi m\u1ecdi l\u1eddi ca t\u1ee5ng. Trong v\u00e0i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, th\u00e0nh t\u00edch c\u1ee7a Kane lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 ghi tr\u00ean 25 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng/m\u00f9a, khi\u1ebfn c\u1eadu \u1ea5y tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o hay b\u1eadc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i th\u00edch \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u, \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf m\u00ecnh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t. \u0110T Anh l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c y\u00eau th\u00edch \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh c\u00fap v\u00e0ng, b\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. Croatia mu\u1ed1n thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, gi\u1ed1ng Argentina, ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec ph\u1ea3i s\u1ee3&rdquo; &ndash; Lovren th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c Harry Kane v\u00e0 Tam S\u01b0.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Quay ng\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 9 th\u00e1ng, Dejan Lovren khi \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed3i t\u1ec7 nh\u1ea5t s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p. Anh li\u00ean t\u1ee5c b\u1ecb Harry Kane v\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Tottenham qua m\u1eb7t, m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn b\u00e0n thua. Ch\u1ec9 30 ph\u00fat sau khi b\u00f3ng l\u0103n, anh b\u1ecb HLV Jurgen Klopp r\u00fat kh\u1ecfi s\u00e2n ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 n\u1ed7i kinh ho\u00e0ng c\u1ee7a Lovren, v\u00e0 anh \u0111ang hy v\u1ecdng \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng di\u1ec5n ra trong tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/dt-croatia-mat-hlv-vi-khieu-khich-chu-nha-nga-421-190822.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/dt-croatia-mat-hlv-vi-khieu-khich-chu-nha-nga.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/dt-croatia-mat-hlv-vi-khieu-khich-chu-nha-nga-421-190822.html\">\u0110T Croatia m\u1ea5t HLV v\u00ec khi\u00eau kh\u00edch ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Nga</span><br>\r\nTr\u1ee3 l\u00fd \u0110T Croatia l\u00e0 \u00f4ng Ognjen Vukojevic m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y v\u1eeba b\u1ecb L\u0110B\u0110 n\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00e0y lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi ban hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 do ch\u1ecdc gi\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hlv-croatia-de-cao-sterling-truoc-tran-ban-ket-gap-dt-anh-421-190780.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/7/hlv-croatia-de-cao-sterling-truoc-tran-ban-ket-gap-dt-anh.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hlv-croatia-de-cao-sterling-truoc-tran-ban-ket-gap-dt-anh-421-190780.html\">HLV Croatia \u0111\u1ec1 cao Sterling tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft g\u1eb7p \u0110T Anh</span><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00e1n k\u1ebft g\u1eb7p \u0110T Anh, HLV Croatia, Zlatko Dalic \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng khi n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 Raheem Sterling, ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Tam...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1103","checkdouble":"190834"},{"date":"10:54 10/07","title":"Buffon: \"Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 s\u1ebd gi\u00fap Neymar m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd h\u01a1n\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/7/buffon-that-bai-tai-world-cup-2018-se-giup-neymar-manh-me-hon.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Bernd Leno m\u1eb7c \u00e1o s\u1ed1 19 \u1edf Arsenal, th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ed1 \u00e1o trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi. Anh r\u1ea5t th\u00edch s\u1ed1 1 nh\u01b0ng s\u1ed1 \u00e1o n\u00e0y \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 Petr Cech.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Bernd Leno ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ch\u1ecdn s\u1ed1 \u00e1o \u1edf Arsenal</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Bayer Leverkusen, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Bernd Leno m\u1eb7c \u00e1o s\u1ed1 1. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 22 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, anh c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t th\u00edch kho\u00e1c l\u00ean m\u00ecnh chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o s\u1ed1 1 \u1edf s\u00e2n Emirates.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Bernd Leno m\u1eb7c \u00e1o s\u1ed1 19 \u1edf Arsenal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Bernd Leno m\u1eb7c \u00e1o s\u1ed1 19 \u1edf Arsenal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/10/tan-binh-bernd-leno-chinh-thuc-chon-so-ao-o-arsenal.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Bernd Leno m\u1eb7c \u00e1o s\u1ed1 19 \u1edf Arsenal</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, Arsenal x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn \u00e1o s\u1ed1 1 \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 Petr Cech, th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi C\u1ed9ng H\u00f2a S\u00e9c \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u1ecf \u00e1o s\u1ed1 33 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111eo \u00e1o s\u1ed1 1 t\u1eeb m\u00f9a 2018/19.\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ed1 \u00e1o nh\u01b0 mong mu\u1ed1n Bernd Leno m\u1eb7c \u00e1o s\u1ed1 19 \u1edf Arsenal, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 \u00e1o c\u00f3 \u00fd ngh\u0129a \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 tu\u1ed5i khi anh ra m\u1eaft Bayer Leverkusen, 19 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 ng\u00e0y ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1992 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u00c1o s\u1ed1 19 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 Santi Cazorla, song c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chia tay \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Emirates.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBernd Leno v\u1eabn c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111eo \u00e1o s\u1ed1 1 \u1edf Arsenal, nh\u01b0ng anh ph\u1ea3i ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ebfn khi Petr Cech r\u1eddi s\u00e2n Emirates. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi S\u00e9c c\u00f2n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 1 n\u0103m v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Leno \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1eadt Petr Cech</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-arsenal-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-tan-binh-thu-3-172-190220.html\" target=\"_blank\">Arsenal mua Leno</span> v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 h\u01a1n 20 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0a th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh n\u00e0y v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb. Petr Cech m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed, song nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng anh s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb cho c\u1ef1u sao Bayer Leverkusen \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Bernd Leno\" title=\"Bernd Leno\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/19/arsenal-sap-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-bernd-leno.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Bernd Leno \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed v\u1edbi Petr Cech</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi s\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh trong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y Leno \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1eadt Petr Cech qua \u0111\u00f3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed s\u1ed1 1 trong khung g\u1ed7. HLV Unai Emery c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1eafp x\u1ebfp \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 hai c\u00f9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, Leno b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh c\u00f2n Cech b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh \u1edf c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00fap. V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c David Ospina s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch t\u00ecm b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi, b\u1edfi \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i anh ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n s\u1ed1 3 c\u1ee7a Arsenal m\u00e0 th\u00f4i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1102","checkdouble":"190835"},{"date":"11:09 10/07","title":"Buffon n\u00f3i g\u00ec tr\u01b0\u1edbc vi\u1ec5n c\u1ea3nh Juve chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Ronaldo?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/10/buffon-noi-gi-truoc-vien-canh-juve-chieu-mo-ronaldo.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, t\u00e2n binh c\u1ee7a CLB PSG \u2013 th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Gianluigi Buffon chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 Ronaldo v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi l\u1ebd t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng.\r\n</h2><h2>Buffon hy v\u1ecdng Ronaldo s\u1edbm sang Juve<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi k\u1ebft th\u00fac m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1edbi ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League th\u1ee9 3 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp, Cris Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho Real Madrid, v\u00e0 \u00fap m\u1edf v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec5n c\u1ea3nh ra \u0111i. Nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y qua, b\u00e1o ch\u00ed \u0111\u1ed3ng lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i th\u00f4ng tin Juventus \u0111ang \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y, v\u00e0 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb n\u1ed5 bom t\u1ea5n 100 tri\u1ec7u euro.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ebfu \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 x\u1ea3y ra, \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tin t\u1ee9c c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 \u0111\u00e1ng m\u1eebng v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Juventus, ngo\u1ea1i tr\u1eeb&hellip; Buffon. Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n 40 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i l\u1eddi chia tay CLB t\u1eeb cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, v\u00e0 m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 2 n\u0103m c\u00f9ng CLB n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p PSG. Ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i c\u00f3 l\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi nh\u1ec7n v\u00e0o l\u00fac n\u00e0y, nh\u01b0ng anh c\u0169ng mong Juve s\u1edbm chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c si\u00eau sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3, \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ecfa m\u00e3n c\u01a1n kh\u00e1t danh hi\u1ec7u C1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Buffon chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 Ronaldo\" title=\"Buffon v\u00e0 Ronaldo\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/10/buffon-noi-gi-truoc-vien-canh-juve-chieu-mo-ronaldo.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Buffon chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 Ronaldo</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean n\u1ebfu Ronaldo gia nh\u1eadp Juventus&rdquo; &ndash; Buffon cho bi\u1ebft. &ldquo;\u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0m t\u00f4i h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac, b\u1edfi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng nh\u01b0 Juve c\u1ea7n, \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ra m\u1ed9t th\u1ea7n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1edbi cho m\u00ecnh.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y x\u1ea3y ra sau khi t\u00f4i ra \u0111i \u01b0, th\u00fa th\u1ef1c t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00ec \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. T\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu v\u1edbi 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u00e0 Ronaldo ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi t\u00f4i \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;T\u00f4i r\u1ea5t hy v\u1ecdng Ronaldo s\u1ebd gia nh\u1eadp Juventus, chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Serie A. \u0110\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 l\u1eddi kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a Juve v\u1edbi ng\u00f4i v\u1ecb s\u1ed1 1&rdquo; &ndash; Buffon chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 Ronaldo.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i ti\u1ebfp theo, trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t, Buffon s\u1ebd l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Ronaldo, n\u1ebfu PSG ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n Juve \u1edf Champions League. V\u00e0 n\u1ebfu si\u00eau sao B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ghi b\u00e0n, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd Buffon s\u1ebd v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i v\u1edbi quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eddi Juve c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.&nbsp;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/tin-chuyen-nhuong/5-thuong-vu-bom-tan-co-the-xay-ra-neu-ronaldo-toi-juventus-187-190765.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/6/5-thuong-vu-bom-tan-co-the-xay-ra-neu-ronaldo-toi-juventus.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/tin-chuyen-nhuong/5-thuong-vu-bom-tan-co-the-xay-ra-neu-ronaldo-toi-juventus-187-190765.html\">5 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 bom t\u1ea5n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra n\u1ebfu Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus</span><br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u cho m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng d\u00e2y chuy\u1ec1n s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/evra-khuyen-ronaldo-tu-choi-mu-gia-nhap-juventus-184-190744.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/9/evra-khuyen-ronaldo-tu-choi-mu-gia-nhap-juventus.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/evra-khuyen-ronaldo-tu-choi-mu-gia-nhap-juventus-184-190744.html\">Evra khuy\u00ean Ronaldo t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i MU, gia nh\u1eadp Juventus</span><br>\r\nPatrice Evra tin r\u1eb1ng Juventus l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o \u0111\u1ec3 Ronaldo ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c chinh ph\u1ee5c nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch trong ph\u1ea7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1101","checkdouble":"190836"},{"date":"11:35 10/07","title":"\u0110\u1ebfn Wenger c\u0169ng s\u1ed1c v\u1edbi Ozil phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n World Cup 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/28/den-wenger-cung-soc-voi-ozil-phien-ban-world-cup-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ngay c\u1ea3 Gi\u00e1o S\u01b0 c\u0169ng kh\u00f3 l\u00f2ng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 c\u1eadu h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u0169 th\u1eddi c\u00f2n d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Arsenal sau khi ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n b\u1ea1c nh\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ee7a anh trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c \u1edf World Cup 2018.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">R\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u t\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed3 \u0111\u00e3 g\u00f3p ph\u1ea7n l\u00e0m n\u00ean th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda l\u1ecbch s\u1eed v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1ee9c khi v\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Joachim Loew s\u1edbm k\u1ebft th\u00fac h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 ng\u00f4i v\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u1edf World Cup 2018 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch nh\u1ee5c nh\u00e3 v\u1edbi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed b\u00e9t b\u1ea3ng l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean sau 80 n\u0103m.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Wenger ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Ozil sa s\u00fat phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1edf World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Wenger ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Ozil sa s\u00fat phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1edf World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/den-wenger-cung-soc-voi-ozil-phien-ban-world-cup-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV\u00a0Wenger ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Ozil m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 hi\u1ec3u cho nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n sa s\u00fat phong \u0111\u1ed9 kh\u00f4ng phanh \u1edf World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Trong s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch n\u1eb7ng n\u1ec1 h\u01a1n c\u1ea3 ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 nh\u1ea1c tr\u01b0\u1edfng Mesut Ozil. Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 g\u00f3i g\u1ecdn chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n s\u00e2n c\u1ecf v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 29 tu\u1ed5i c\u00f2n d\u00ednh l\u00edu nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 b\u00ean l\u1ec1 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1ng c\u00f3, nh\u01b0 c\u00e3i nhau tay \u0111\u00f4i v\u1edbi C\u0110V hay ch\u1ee5p h\u00ecnh chung v\u1edbi t\u1ed5ng th\u1ed1ng Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3 trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m ch\u00ednh tr\u1ecb.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u0110\u1ebfn th\u1ebf n\u00e0y, ngay c\u1ea3 HLV Arsene Wenger c\u0169ng kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 c\u1eadu h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u0169 c\u01b0ng chi\u1ec1u th\u1eddi c\u00f2n d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Arsenal. Gi\u00e1o S\u01b0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p m\u1edbi ph\u1ea3i \u0111au l\u00f2ng ch\u00ea tr\u00e1ch Ozil phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n World Cup 2018: \u201cTheo d\u00f5i Mesut thi \u0111\u1ea5u, t\u00f4i c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ch\u1ecbu \u00e1p l\u1ef1c l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ebfn n\u1ed7i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n l\u00e0 ch\u00ednh m\u00ecnh. C\u00f3 nh\u1eefng khi n\u00ean d\u00e2ng cao ch\u01a1i tr\u1ef1c di\u1ec7n h\u01a1n, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u1ea1i y\u00ean v\u1ecb m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch c\u1ea7u to\u00e0n th\u00e1i qu\u00e1.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cTh\u00f4i n\u00e0o, \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e2u ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 Ozil m\u00e0 t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft, l\u00e0 Ozil c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ef1 tin l\u00e0m kh\u1ed5 v\u00e0 k\u1ebft li\u1ec5u \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 Ozil m\u00e0 t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn ra \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u1eefa r\u1ed3i. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng v\u1edbi kh\u00f4ng ch\u00fat thanh tho\u00e1t, t\u1ef1 do n\u00e0o h\u1ebft v\u00e0 c\u1ee9 nh\u01b0 th\u1ec3 \u0111ang b\u1ecb c\u00e1i g\u00ec \u0111\u00f3 ki\u1ec1m h\u00e3m l\u1ea1i m\u1ed7i khi c\u00f3 b\u00f3ng trong ch\u00e2n.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cD\u00f9 g\u00ec th\u00ec t\u00f4i c\u0169ng bi\u1ebft, Ozil v\u1eabn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u01b0ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 Gundogan \u0111\u1ec1u v\u01b0\u1edbng v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng r\u1eafc r\u1ed1i ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m World Cup. B\u1ecdn h\u1ecd g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 b\u1ecb ph\u1ec9 b\u00e1ng \u1edf \u0110\u1ee9c trong khi c\u00e1i c\u1ea7n l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 th\u00ec l\u1ea1i ch\u1eb3ng th\u1ea5y \u0111\u00e2u, d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i cho c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n v\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 sa s\u00fat c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/goc-nhin-world-cup-2018/dt-duc-bi-loai-tu-vong-bang-dau-roi-tinh-than-duc-466-189832.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/28/dt-duc-bi-loai-tu-vong-bang-dau-roi-tinh-than-duc.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/goc-nhin-world-cup-2018/dt-duc-bi-loai-tu-vong-bang-dau-roi-tinh-than-duc-466-189832.html\">Mannschaft b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i ngay t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng: \u0110\u00e2u r\u1ed3i tinh th\u1ea7n \u0110\u1ee9c?</span><br>\r\n\u0110\u00e2u r\u1ed3i tinh th\u1ea7n \u0110\u1ee9c? Mannschaft r\u1eddi World Cup 2018 trong s\u1ef1 y\u1ebfu nh\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u00e0 Mesut Ozil th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n \u0111i\u1ec3n h\u00ecnh cho m\u1ed9t Mannschaft thi\u1ebfu b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1100","checkdouble":"190839"}]}